ers.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/526GameTimes1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/526GameTimes1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>Game Times</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/526GameTimes1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 14:55:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>2</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59139</s:story_id></item><item><title>Limited Amount of NCAA Morgantown Regional Tickets Available Now</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/baseball-limited-amount-of-ncaa-morgantown-regional-tickets-available-now</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/baseball-limited-amount-of-ncaa-morgantown-regional-tickets-available-now</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Regional Tickets on sale graphic" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. - The West Virginia University baseball team has earned the No. 16 overall seed in the 2026 NCAA Baseball Championship and will host the NCAA Morgantown Regional at Kendrick Family Ballpark this Friday, May 29 through Monday, June 1.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg"><media:title>Regional Tickets on sale graphic</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/BB26_NCAARegTixOnSale_1920x1080_Generic__1_.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 14:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59137</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Set for NCAA East First Round</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/track-field-mountaineers-set-for-ncaa-east-first-round</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/track-field-mountaineers-set-for-ncaa-east-first-round</guid><category>Track &amp; Field</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Mercy Kinyanjui competing at the Big 12 Outdoor Track and Field Championships" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University track and field team travels to Lexington, Kentucky, for the 2026 NCAA East First Round.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg"><media:title>Mercy Kinyanjui competing at the Big 12 Outdoor Track and Field Championships</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/285A5020__1_.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 12:21:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>16</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59138</s:story_id></item><item><title>Parking Information for NCAA Morgantown Regional</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/baseball-parking-information-for-ncaa-morgantown-regional</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/27/baseball-parking-information-for-ncaa-morgantown-regional</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="An overhead shot of Kendrick Family Ballpark during a West Virginia baseball game" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/27/RMB_2994.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. - The West Virginia University baseball team will open NCAA Regional play against Binghamton on Friday, May 29, at 5 p.m. ET, on ESPN+, while Wake Forest and Kentucky will meet in Friday's first game, at 12 p.m. ET on ESPN2. The Morgantown Regional will continue with games at 12 p.m. and 5 p.m. on Saturday and Sunday, with Monday's game time being released later this week if necessary.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/RMB_2994.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/RMB_2994.jpg"><media:title>An overhead shot of Kendrick Family Ballpark during a West Virginia baseball game</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/27/RMB_2994.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2026 11:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59136</s:story_id></item><item><title>Morgantown Regional Set as West Virginia Earns No. 16 National Seed</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/25/baseball-morgantown-regional-set-as-west-virginia-earns-no-16-national-seed</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/25/baseball-morgantown-regional-set-as-west-virginia-earns-no-16-national-seed</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Morgantown Regional Bracket" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/25/BB26_NCAARegBracket_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University baseball team has earned the No. 16 national seed and learned the three other teams that will play in the 2026 NCAA Morgantown Regional from May 29-June 1, at Kendrick Family Ballpark.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/25/BB26_NCAARegBracket_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/25/BB26_NCAARegBracket_1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>Morgantown Regional Bracket</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/25/BB26_NCAARegBracket_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 15:34:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59133</s:story_id></item><item><title>Frequent Flyer West Virginia to Begin NCAA Tournament Play in Morgantown</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/25/baseball-frequent-flyer-west-virginia-to-begin-ncaa-tournament-play-in-morgantown</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/25/baseball-frequent-flyer-west-virginia-to-begin-ncaa-tournament-play-in-morgantown</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="The West Virginia University baseball team watches its name come up on the board for the 2026 NCAA Tournament during its team watch party at The Goat Country Roads Pub in Morgantown, West Virginia, on Monday, May 25, 2026. " src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/25/Team-Main.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University baseball team certainly knows its way around America's airports.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/25/Team-Main.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/25/Team-Main.jpg"><media:title>The West Virginia University baseball team watches its name come up on the board for the 2026 NCAA Tournament during its team watch party at The Goat Country Roads Pub in Morgantown, West Virginia, on Monday, May 25, 2026. </media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/25/Team-Main.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 15:26:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59132</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Selected to Host NCAA Baseball Regional</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/24/west-virginia-selected-to-host-ncaa-baseball-regional</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/24/west-virginia-selected-to-host-ncaa-baseball-regional</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Baseball Hosting Graphic" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/24/BB26_WeAreHostingNCAA_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University baseball team has been selected to host an NCAA Baseball Regional for the third time in program history.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/24/BB26_WeAreHostingNCAA_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/24/BB26_WeAreHostingNCAA_1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>Baseball Hosting Graphic</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/24/BB26_WeAreHostingNCAA_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 20:53:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59131</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Fall to Kansas in Big 12 Title Game</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/24/baseball-mountaineers-fall-to-kansas-in-big-12-title-game</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/5/24/baseball-mountaineers-fall-to-kansas-in-big-12-title-game</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Ian Korn throws a pitch against Kansas" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/5/23/DSC03198.jpeg" /><br /><br />SURPRISE, Ariz. – The ninth-ranked and No. 2-seed West Virginia University baseball team fell to 13th-ranked and No. 1-seed Kansas, 9-0, in the Big 12 Tournament final, Saturday afternoon at Surprise Stadium. The Mountaineers fall to 39-14 while the Jayhawks complete the Big 12 double and improve to 42-16.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/23/DSC03198.jpeg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/23/DSC03198.jpeg"><media:title>Ian Korn throws a pitch against Kansas</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/5/23/DSC03198.jpeg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 00:03:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>1</s:sport_id><s:story_id>59130</s:story_id></item></channel></rss>